were made by the Big Three American automakers.

384
00:12:19,540 --> 00:12:21,810
而这三大车企全部把自己的总部
ér zhè sān dà chē qǐ quán bù bǎ zì jǐ de zǒng bù
And all three of these major automakers had their headquarters...

385
00:12:21,810 --> 00:12:23,230
建立在这个城市
