the more money they lost.

404
00:12:59,060 --> 00:13:01,080
所以呢就逼着大家最终的把产业转移
suǒ yǐ ne jiù bī zhe dà jiā zuì zhōng de bǎ chǎn yè zhuǎn yí
So, this ultimately forced everyone to relocate their industries.

405
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:04,450
那要不然就往美国南方没有汽车工会的州转移
nà yào bù rán jiù wǎng měi guó nán fāng méi yǒu qì chē gōng huì de zhōu zhuǎn yí
Or, they'd move to the southern states in the U.S. where there were no auto unions.

406
00:13:04,450 --> 00:13:06,430
要不然呢就往国外转
