Or, they'd move their operations overseas.

407
00:13:06,430 --> 00:13:09,250
所以底特律市呢也从当年人口最辉煌的
suǒ yǐ dǐ tè lǜ shì ne yě cóng dāng nián rén kǒu zuì huī huáng de
So, as a result, Detroit's population, which was once at its peak...

408
00:13:09,250 --> 00:13:12,220
180万人口一直降到降降降降降降降
180 wàn rén kǒu yì zhí jiàng dào jiàng jiàng jiàng jiàng jiàng jiàng jiàng
From a peak of 1.8 million people, it just kept dropping, and dropping, and dropping...

409
00:13:12,220 --> 00:13:13,440
抑制人口外移
yì zhì rén kǒu wài yí
to stop the population from leaving.

410
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:14,700
然后逃离这个城市
rán hòu táo lí zhè ge chéng shì
and flee the city.

411
00:13:14,700 --> 00:13:15,620
最终的这个城市
zuì zhōng de zhè ge chéng shì
And this city, in the end...

412
00:13:15,620 --> 00:13:17,080
现在目前人口呢只有70万人
xiàn zài mù qián rén kǒu ne zhǐ yǒu 70 wàn rén
And now, the population is only 700,000.

413
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:17,680
当然了
dāng rán le
Of course.

414
00:13:17,680 --> 00:13:20,520
这个工会是造成美国汽车行业没落的
zhè ge gōng huì shì zào chéng měi guó qì chē háng yè mò luò de
This union is one of the reasons for the decline of the American auto industry.

415
00:13:20,520 --> 00:13:21,580
主要原因之一啊
zhǔ yào yuán yīn zhī yī a
That's one of the main reasons,

416
00:13:21,580 --> 00:13:22,440
那还有一个原因呢
nà hái yǒu yí gè yuán yīn ne
So, what's the other reason?

417
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:25,510
就是来自全世界各地汽车行业
jiù shì lái zì quán shì jiè gè dì qì chē háng yè
And that's the competition from the auto industries all around the world.

418
00:13:25,510 --> 00:13:27,170
对美国汽车行业的冲击
duì měi guó qì chē háng yè de chōng jī
on the American auto industry.

419
00:13:27,170 --> 00:13:28,350
比如像日企对吧
