And today, it goes without saying that the situation is even more severe.

421
00:13:30,370 --> 00:13:32,400
来自中国的这些汽车行业
lái zì zhōng guó de zhè xiē qì chē háng yè
And now you have the auto industry from China.

422
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:35,760
对整个全球汽车行业的冲击都是不可估量的
duì zhěng gè quán qiú qì chē háng yè de chōng jī dōu shì bù kě gū liáng de
The impact on the entire global auto industry has been immeasurable.

423
00:13:35,760 --> 00:13:37,800
所以来自内部薪资的问题呢
suǒ yǐ lái zì nèi bù xīn zī de wèn tí ne
So, what about the internal issue of wages?

424
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:39,060
是他们自己内部的原因
shì tā men zì jǐ nèi bù de yuán yīn
These were problems from within.

425
00:13:39,060 --> 00:13:41,100
那来自外部的更是降维打击
nà lái zì wài bù de gèng shì jiàng wéi dǎ jī
And the external factors? They were a whole different, devastating kind of blow.

426
00:13:41,100 --> 00:13:42,020
两块一相加
liǎng kuài yī xiāng jiā
Put those two together,

427
00:13:42,020 --> 00:13:44,300
导致现在底特律呢就成了你现在看到这
dǎo zhì xiàn zài dǐ tè lǜ ne jiù chéng le nǐ xiàn zài kàn dào zhè
And that's what led to Detroit becoming what you see today.

428
00:13:44,300 --> 00:13:46,960
这也是这个城市从他们巅峰的时候
zhè yě shì zhè ge chéng shì cóng tā men diān fēng de shí hòu
And this is how the city went from its peak,

429
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:48,220
